#: src/freqplots/freqplots_core.c:761
msgid ""
"Excitation-port selector: models with more than one EX excitation list every "
"port here.\n"
"\n"
"Entry P<n>: T<tag>/S<seg>\n"
"    n = port number, tag = NEC tag, seg = segment.\n"
"\n"
"Hover an entry to preview that port, click to\n"
"select it, or click away to keep the current one.\n"
"\n"
"Charts that follow the selected port:\n"
"    • Z real / imag\n"
"    • Z magnitude / phase\n"
"    • Smith\n"
"    • VSWR / S11\n"
"    • Net-gain traces (Gain and Viewer gain)\n"
"\n"
"Whole-antenna charts, unaffected by the port:\n"
"    • raw Max gain, Gain direction, F/B\n"
"    • Antenna temperature, G/T"
msgstr ""
"Pemilih port pengujaan: model dengan lebih daripada satu EX menyenaraikan "
"setiap port di sini.\n"
"\n"
"Entri P<n>: T<tag>/S<seg>\n"
"    n = nombor port, tag = tag NEC, seg = segmen.\n"
"\n"
"Layangkan kursor pada satu entri untuk pratonton port itu, klik untuk\n"
"memilihnya, atau klik di luar untuk mengekalkan yang semasa.\n"
"\n"
"Carta yang mengikut port terpilih:\n"
"    • Z nyata / khayalan\n"
"    • Magnitud / fasa Z\n"
"    • Smith\n"
"    • VSWR / S11\n"
"    • Trek gandaan bersih (Gandaan dan Gandaan Pemerhati)\n"
"\n"
"Carta seluruh antena, tidak terjejas oleh port:\n"
"    • Gandaan Maksimum mentah, Arah gandaan, F/B\n"
"    • Suhu antena, G/T"

